{"tid":163953,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"真係開始覺得連登同高登都係不要分得那麼細","createTime":"2017-03-20T10:49:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-23T13:18:15.000Z","uid":18271,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1524847cf20efa31f5c5a6ecccac68873450e363","tid":163953,"uid":18271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T10:49:45.000Z","msg":"成日有班柒頭不學無術<br />\n乜撚都唔識喺度扮專家<br />\n無咩特別既誤導左人都算數<br />\n關乎人命嗰d好撚心你講少句啦on9<br />\n好似呢個post <br />\n<br />\n30歲男觀塘墮樓喪命 母哭斷腸<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/163391/page/1?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/163391/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n有條撚樣講到情緒病無得教<br />\n醫生俾你食藥係想搵錢咁<br />\n你條毒撚仲叻過醫生<br />\n咁把炮拎左諾貝爾獎啦<br />\n<br />\n後來唔上高登都係因為唔想睇呢d垃圾言論<br />\n點知開左連登都係一柒樣"},{"pid":"d6d1e4aadfe781bb19c453aecc51f5880c1a7ca5","tid":163953,"uid":18271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T10:52:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/20/185149_50136f9a731f164325fa38dc2ac61292.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F20%2F185149_50136f9a731f164325fa38dc2ac61292.jpg&h=af52c47b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有情緒病唔好睇<br />\n醫生話你有開藥俾你食都無用<br />\n真係有病睇完又信左真係害死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"541bfe8987680cdd43f25337b5268c79f84c09e3","tid":163953,"uid":9681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T10:55:50.000Z","msg":"sor 畀錯負皮"},{"pid":"bbfd3feec515fdcca70051235eace28c9873d6bf","tid":163953,"uid":18271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T10:57:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>sor 畀錯負皮</blockquote><br />\n就咁睇topic係好易，唔緊要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67905aeca2452269f3c58e1846a4aebde8d843a0","tid":163953,"uid":706,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T10:59:05.000Z","ms